title: Dudley Cafe
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, American, Indian, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Asian, Bakery, Fusion, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Cafe located across from Dudley Station in the Bruce Bolling municipal building in Dudley Square. Offers sandwiches, salads, rice bowls, pastries, coffee, and grab and go. Dishes are a medley of East Asian, American, and Indian food. Hosts community events like trivia nights and poetry readings. Vegan (vg) and vegetarian (v) items are labelled.
